{META_DATA}: BLACK SCREEN:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. RIVER ANDUIN - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: SMEAGOL and his cousin, DEAGOL, sit in a SMALL CORACLE, their FISHING LINES draped over the side . . . SUNSHINE glinting off the surface of the water.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: An idyllic image.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SUDDENLY . . . DEAGOL's FISHING ROD BENDS under the weight of a LARGE FISH.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DEAGOL
{META_DATA}: (excited)
{DIALOGUE}: Smeagol, I've got one!
{META_DATA}: (he laughs)
{DIALOGUE}: I've got a fish, Smeagol!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SMEAGOL
{META_DATA}: (excitedly)
{DIALOGUE}: Go on, pull it in.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DEAGOL pulls on his ROD, but is HAULED OVERBOARD and disappears underwater with a SPLASH!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: SMEAGOL leaning over the BOAT . . . CONCERNED.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SMEAGOL (cont'd)
{META_DATA}: (worried)
{DIALOGUE}: Deagol!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. UNDERWATER, RIVER ANDUIN - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: DEAGOL is towed to the RIVER BED by a LARGE FISH . . . he suddenly lets go of the line . . . eyes fixed on a SHINING GOLD RING, lying in 'the SILT.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Final Revision - October, 2003 2
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. RIVER ANDUIN, GLADDEN FIELDS - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: DEAGOL climbs out of the WATER, onto the RIVER BANK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: the RING revealed in DEAGOL'S PALM . . .
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: SMEAGOL peers over his shoulder . . . the GOLD reflects in SMEAGOL'S EYES!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ON SOUNDTRACK: The HUM of the RING growing LOUDER . . .
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SMEAGOL
{DIALOGUE}: Give us that, Deagol, my love!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DEAGOL turns to look at him, a smirk on his face.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DEAGOL
{DIALOGUE}: Why?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: SMEAGOL moves towards DEAGOL . . .
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SMEAGOL
{DIALOGUE}: Because its my birthday, and I wants it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: SMEAGOL jumps on DEAGOL . . . STRANGLING HIM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SMEAGOL rips the GLITTERING RING from DEAGOL'S LIMP HAND.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SMEAGOL (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: My precious!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: SMEAGOL slips the RING onto his FINGER and DISAPPEARS.
