{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Upon its out- thrust knee is the Guarded City: MINAS TIRITH.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: With SEVEN WALLS OF WHITE STONE, so strong and old that it seems to have been not built, MINAS TIRITH looks carven by giants out of the bones of the earth.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GANDALF
{DIALOGUE}: Minas Tirith . . . City of the Kings.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Suddenly the SUN climbs over the eastern hills, and sends forth a SHAFT OF SUNLIGHT that GLEAMS against th e face of the CITY.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The TOWER OF ECTHELION stands high within the topmost walls.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WHITE BANNERS break and FLUTTER from the BATTLEMENTS in the morning breeze.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. MINAS TIRITH STREETS - DAY
