{DIALOGUE}: Final Revision - October, 2003 29.
{META_DATA}: CONTINUED:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: The stares of frightened GONDORIANS as GANDALF and PIPPIN gallop through the WINDING STREETS . . .
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: AERIAL SHOT: SHADOWFAX, carrying GANDALF and PIPPIN up towards the 7th LEVEL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: MINAS TIRITH is built in 7 LEVELS - each behind a CIRCULAR DEFENSIVE WALL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Each level rises - the city reaches a height of nearly 1000 FEET on its TOPMOST LEVEL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A towering BASTION of NATURAL ROCK - shaped like a sharp ship's prow - bisects the city from the 2nd LEVEL to the TOP.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. MINAS TIRITH, COURT OF THE KINGS - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SHADOWFAX arrives at a GREAT CITADEL on the SUMMIT of the CITY - 1000 FEET above the PELENNOR FIELDS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: GANDALF and PIPPIN dismount, leaving the GUARDS of the CITADEL to tend to SHADOWFAX.
