{DIALOGUE}: Alight, I'm sorry, I didn't mean for it to go so far, I was so angry . . . Here, let's rest up a bit.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SAM attempts to fuss around FRODO ...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRODO
{META_DATA}: (exhausted)
{DIALOGUE}: I ' m alright.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAM
{DIALOGUE}: No, no, you're not alright!
{DIALOGUE}: You're exhausted!
{DIALOGUE}: It's that Gollum; it's this place; it's that thing around your neck.
{DIALOGUE}: I could help a bit . . . I could carry it for a while - share the load.
