{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRODO
{DIALOGUE}: Get away!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FRODO pushes SAM away, clutching at the RING beneath his shirt
{META_DATA}: (CONTINUED)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Final Revision - October, 2003 58.
{META_DATA}: CONTINUED: ( 4 )
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAM
{META_DATA}: (confused)
{DIALOGUE}: I don't want to keep it . . . I just want to help!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FRODO rises to his FEET, as if empowered with a frightening intense ENERGY.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GOLLUM
{DIALOGUE}: See!
{DIALOGUE}: See!
{DIALOGUE}: He wants it for himself.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAM
{META_DATA}: (beside himself)
{DIALOGUE}: Shut up, you!
{DIALOGUE}: Go away.
{DIALOGUE}: Get out of here.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: FRODO ...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRODO
