{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: TWO great clusters of many-windowed EYES protrude from her bulbous head.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Her LEGS are bent, with a 12 FOOT SPAN and HAIRS that stick out like steel spines.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Her HUGE, SWOLLEN BODY, a vast bloated bag, sways and sags between her legs.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Her age-old BLACK HIDE is knobbly and pitted, blotchy with LIVID MARKS . . . but her belly underneath is PALE and LUMINOUS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SHELOB beats the air with her FORELEGS.
