{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ARWEN, eyes shining ... MORTAL now, but deeply in love ... carrying the STANDARD of CONDOR ... ARAGORN kisses her
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ELROND looks on . . . his face breaks into a smile.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ARAGORN and ARWEN embrace.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ARAGORN and ARWEN walking through the CROWD towards four SMALL FIGURES who stand nervously at the end of the AVENUE . . .
