{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILBO O.S.
{META_DATA}: (frail)
{DIALOGUE}: Tell me again, lad.
{DIALOGUE}: Where are we going?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRODO O.S.
{DIALOGUE}: To the harbour, Bilbo.
{DIALOGUE}: The Elves have accorded you a special honour.
{DIALOGUE}: A place on the last ship to leave Middle-earth.
