{DIALOGUE}: Elanor!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He hugs his daughter . . .
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRODO V/0
{DIALOGUE}: My dear Sam.
{DIALOGUE}: You cannot always be torn in two.
{DIALOGUE}: You have to be one and whole for many years.
{DIALOGUE}: You have so much enjoy and to be and to do.
{DIALOGUE}: Because Sam, your part in the journey goes on.
