{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAM
{DIALOGUE}: Hello, little Frodo!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: SAM with his FAMILY . . . he draws a deep breath:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAM (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: Well ... I'm back.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SAM looks at his LOVELY FAMILY with GREAT HAPPINESS, tinged with a little SADNESS . . .
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SAM and ROSIE take the CHILDREN'S HANDS and enter BAGSHOT . . . the BRIGHT YELLOW DOORWAY closes behind them.
{META_DATA}: FADE TO BLACK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Final Revision - October, 2003 151.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: THE END.
